VA mir Khusro Sangeet Academy, a Chennai based non-profit organisation committed to promoting Hindustani music, is presenting the 11-year-old Sufi qawwal Asad Irfaan Sabri, on December 1, at The Museum Theatre, Egmore. The NGO provides financial support to the physically challenged and retired artists. Founded by singer Janab Munna Shaokath Ali, the academy has instituted a lifetime achievement award and also promotes seasoned and up and coming artists through concerts and baithaks.
